Package goal.tools.mc.core.lmhashset

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    LMMap<K>
    A "less memory" version (hence "LM") of Map, whose each entry is a key rather than a key-value pair.
    LMMap.Entry<K>
    A map entry (key-value pair).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LMAbstractMap<K>
    A "less memory" version (hence "LM") of AbstractMap, whose each entry is a key rather than a key-value pair.
    LMAbstractMap.SimpleEntry<K>
    An Entry maintaining a key and a value.
    LMAbstractMap.SimpleImmutableEntry<K>
    An Entry maintaining an immutable key and value.
    LMHashSet<K>
    A "less memory" version (hence "LM") of HashSet, whose implementation is largely based on HashMap.
